Sigma Rules
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The Sigma rules embedded in this software are derived from the SigmaHQ repository
(https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma).

Copyright (c) SigmaHQ Contributors

License: Detection Rule License (DRL) 1.1
https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/LICENSE.Detection.Rules.md

Summary of DRL 1.1 terms:
- You may use, copy, and distribute these detection rules, including in commercial
  products.
- You must preserve the license notice and attribution.
- You must not claim authorship of the original Sigma rules.
- Modified rules must be clearly marked as such.
- The license does NOT cover the Sigma specification itself (which is MIT-licensed).

The embedded rules are a curated subset selected for intrusion detection purposes.
Rule files are located at: internal/sigma/rules/

